-- 2010-10-13T02:38:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/pertamina-buys-nigerian-bonny-light-crude-for-december-delivery-from-vitol.html
PT Pertamina , Indonesia’s state oil
company, purchased two cargoes of Nigeria’s Bonny Light crude
from Vitol Group for delivery in December, said two traders who
participate in the market.  Details of the purchase are as follows:  To contact the reporter on this story:
